                    "effect": "You cause the arm to become corporeal until the end of your turn, allowing you to use it to make Strikes or grasp objects. It remains corporeal if you\u2019re holding an item or it\u2019s wearing an item at the end of your turn. Your unarmed attack Strikes made with the aether appendage are magical . If they\u2019re already magical, they instead gain the effect of the  *ghost touch* property rune.",
